<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BtrBlocks - Better building blocks for the cloud</title>

    {#- Add an arbitrary string to the bundle #}
    {%- css %}{% include "public/css/base.css" %}{% endcss %}
    <style>{% getBundle "css" %}</style>

    <style>

        body {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        header {
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        .hero {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 4rem 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .hero::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1), rgba(0, 204, 255, 0.05));
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo-img {
            height: 2.2rem;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        .slogan {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .description {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .principles {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }
        
        .principle-box {
            background-color: var(--background-color-secondary);
            border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-90);
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 2rem;
            width: 300px;
            text-align: left;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .principle-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .principle-box h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .principle-box p {
        }
        
        .icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-right: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .subscribe-form {
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .subscribe-form input {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-20);
            color: white;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            border-radius: 4px 0 0 4px;
        }
        
        .subscribe-form input::placeholder {
        }
        
        .subscribe-form input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .subscribe-btn {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .subscribe-btn:hover {
            background-color: #0052CC;
        }
        
        .mission {
            background-color: var(--code-bg);
            padding: 4rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-20);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-20);
        }
        
        .mission h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .mission p {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .code-comment {
            color: #6A9955;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
        }
        
        footer {
            padding: 2rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .principles {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .slogan {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .description {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            
            .subscribe-form {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .subscribe-form input {
                border-radius: 4px;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }
            
            .subscribe-btn {
                border-radius: 4px;
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">
                {%- from 'img/logo.svg' import logo %}
                {{ logo({ class: 'logo-img' }) }}
                BtrBlocks
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-content">
            <h1 class="slogan">Better building blocks for the cloud</h1>
            <p class="description">Cloud apps are currently built on legacy tech and locked in hyperscalers' silos. BtrBlocks solves this by building foundational cloud-independent infrastructure services.</p>
            <form class="subscribe-form">
                <input type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
                <button type="submit" class="subscribe-btn">Subscribe</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="container">
        <div class="principles">
            <div class="principle-box">
                <h3>Cloud-Independent</h3>
                <p>Break free from vendor lock-in with infrastructure services that work seamlessly across all major cloud providers. No proprietary APIs. No migration headaches.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="principle-box">
                <h3>Cloud-Native</h3>
                <p>Built for distributed systems from the ground up. Embraces containerization, microservices architecture, and dynamic orchestration without the complexity.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="principle-box">
                <h3>Modern Technology</h3>
                <p>Engineered with cutting-edge tech stacks to deliver significantly better performance, reliability, and scalability metrics that legacy solutions can't match.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="mission">
        <div class="container">
            <span class="code-comment">/* Our mission */</span>
            <h2>Breaking down cloud silos</h2>
            <p>Current cloud is built on legacy tech and captured in silos. We are building foundational cloud-independent infrastructure services for cloud-native applications.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2025 BtrBlocks. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
